hibit was horrible, unless you have never seen a lion before. The only time i had to wait for an elevator was on Sunday when it seemed like the whole hotel was checking out. Monday it was a totally different crowd, lots of older people and families. Overall I had an excellent stay. It was worth the money and would stay again if i was looking to save a buck!!	
